Interface StreamingDataOutput<S extends StreamingDataOutput<S>>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    StreamingCommon<S>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Bytes<Underlying>, BytesOut<Underlying>, ByteStringAppender<B>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractBytes, GuardedNativeBytes, HexDumpBytes, MappedBytes, NativeBytes, NativeBytes.NativeSubBytes, OnHeapBytes, SubBytes, UncheckedBytes, UncheckedNativeBytes, VanillaBytes

    public interface StreamingDataOutput<S extends StreamingDataOutput<S>>
extends StreamingCommon<S>
    Position based access. Once data has been read, the position() moves.

    The use of this instance is single threaded, though the use of the data
